com.digi.xbee.api.listeners

Interface IIPDataReceiveListener


  • public interface IIPDataReceiveListener
    This interface defines the required methods that should be implemented to behave as an IP data listener and be notified when new IP data is received.
    Since:
    1.2.0

        Called when IP data is received.
        Parameters:
        ipMessage - An IPMessage object containing the data, the IP address that sent the data, the source and destination ports and the IPProtocol of the transmission.
